≤In abiding and loving memory of LORRAINE KNOWLES
October 1948 - December 2022, now with the angels.
She loved this church and her church family, and was loved by all who had the privilege of coming into contact with her.
Our loss is the angels' gain.
Rest in eternal peace my darling soulmate Lorraine."ÿ
